25|$|A common {{source of}} {{economic}} {{information for the}} first section of the <b>business</b> <b>valuation</b> report is the Federal Reserve Board's Beige Book, published eight times a year by the Federal Reserve Bank. State governments and industry associations also publish useful statistics describing regional and industry conditions.|$|E
